Package org.netbeans.beaninfo.editors

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StringArrayCustomizable
    An interface for PropertyEditor that wishes to use StringArrayCustomEditor as its custom editor.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanEditor
    Editor for property of type java.lang.Boolean
    BoolEditor
    Replacement editor for boolean primitive values which supports internationalization and alternate string values that can be supplied to the property editor via adding an array returning an array of two Strings (false then true) from env.getFeatureDescriptor().getValue().

  • Exception Summary
